description: Going on an interview was never fun for Casey Everett but he was looking forward to meeting with a wealthy gentleman, Deep Dic, to be his assistant. After listening to what he had to say and taking one look at Deep, Casey knew he would have to work his ass off for this position. Deep Dic doesn't disappoint in making Casey understand what kind of work might be required from time to time. Casey definitely "Nailed It" by taking that big, thick, black dick and landed himself a new position he'll be very happy with.
title: Nailed It
